.TH XDC-NODE-SETUP 1 "February 2026" "XDC Node Setup 2.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
xdc-node-setup \- Production-ready XDC Network node deployment toolkit
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B setup.sh
[\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B xdc-node-setup
is a comprehensive toolkit for deploying XDC Network nodes on Linux and macOS.
It supports multiple deployment modes including Docker, Kubernetes, and bare-metal.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-\-advanced
Enable advanced configuration mode with custom options
.TP
.BR \-\-simple
Use simple mode with default settings (default)
.TP
.BR \-\-help 